                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18311020-184-victim1252 t18311020-184-viclabel980"></join>. On the 14th of October, the prisoner came to the tap, and asked for something - she then went away, and in about a quarter of an hour I missed a candlestick - I followed her, saw her put her hand into her pocket, and I saw this candlestick slip half way out of her pocket.</p>
